Package: quickGrid
Title: Quick method for grid-based crime prediction.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Giovanni",
           family = "Circo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "gmcirco42@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4309-1884"))
Description: Provides a quick method for making crime forecasts using a grid-based design. 
    Functions to calculate distances, densities, and grid counts. Implements 'XGBoost' for estimation of
    crime predictions.
